    "Specifically, RC models can include adaptive homeostatic mechanisms that regulate Fig. 4 | Toolbox components.",
    "Perceptual decision making (left column): is a twoalternative forced choice task (y = {1, 2}) in which the reservoir must be able to integrate two stimuli (x 2 and x 3; x 1 serves as a bias) to decide which one is higher on average.",
